#  Cortex: Courier Agent (STARTER)

<!--
  Courier agent: Read-only operations only. Qwen 1.5B running on iGPU.
  Use for search, query, manifest lookup, ledger read operations.
-->

##  STEP 0  Do this BEFORE any action
> 1. Check the Regression Buffer table below
> 2. If similar to a previous error - advise the user
> 3. Confirm: "I will work on [MODULE/FILE] only"
> 4. **ENFORCE**: Courier is READ-ONLY only. No write operations allowed.

##  Essential Workspace Map

| File/Dir | Alias | Purpose |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `neocortex_config.yaml` | `$cfg` | Courier-specific configuration |
| `DIR-CORE-FR-001-core-central/.agents/rules/` | `@rules` | Rules directory |
| `memory_ledger_courier.json` | `$MEM` | Courier state ledger |

##  Compact Encoding (MANDATORY)
>  `"$main section X"` |  `"full/path/to/file.ext section X"`

| $ = file | @ = directory | ! = command | ? = pattern |

##  Essential Commands

| Alias | Real Command |
| :--- | :--- |
| `!start` | `python -m neocortex.mcp.sub_server --port 11435 --lobe-dir "lobes/courier" --tools "lobes,manifest,ledger" --role courier` |
| `!backup` | `$ts=(Get-Date -Format 'yyyyMMdd_HHmmss'); Copy-Item $MEM backup\$ts.json` |
| `!token-check` | `$json = Get-Content memory_ledger_courier.json -Raw; Write-Host "Tokens: $([math]::Round($json.Length/4))"` |

##  NEVER DO (Courier-specific)
- **Rewrite any file** - courier is READ-ONLY
- **Execute write actions**: neocortex_lobes.create, neocortex_lobes.update, neocortex_kg.add_entity
- **Modify configuration** - read config only
- **Spawn other agents** - courier cannot orchestrate
- **Execute shell commands** - security restriction

##  ALLOWED ACTIONS ONLY
- `neocortex_lobes.search` - Search lobes only
- `neocortex_manifest.query` - Query manifest
- `neocortex_ledger.get_metrics` - Read metrics
- `neocortex_task.execute` - Execute read-only tasks

